<br>
   Me and my real life girlfriend are new to Firiona Vie.  We met on Prexus server 4 years ago and are now living together in real life.  Shortly before Kunark came out, we moved to the Test Server as we much prefered the low population there.  (At that time, 400 people on at peak hours was a lot of people for Test.)  We remained there until about last week when I finally had lost interest in playing there.  During our time on Test, she had a Druid and Cleric both 50+ and I have had a 60+ Druid and 50+ warrior so we have a good knowledge of the game.<br>
<br>
   What made me decide to leave Test?  One of the main reasons that I liked Test in the beginning was the friendlyness and helpfullness of the people there when I started out.  Once you got to around level 20, the older Test players figured you would be staying around awhile and would help you in any way they could.  (I know waiting for level 20, especially back then, seems a little overkill but too many people would leave Test long before then do to all the bugs and server outages.)  In conjunction with that, back then, your reputation was everything on Test.  If you were a loot whore or just a plain ole jerk, you would find it extremely hard to get a group.  Unfortunately, this has changed there.  Too many of the original people left Test, some due to the I-Wipe and many from just losing interest in the game itself.  In order for the high-end guilds to keep going, they started relaxing their unwritten rules on behavior and it trickled down across all levels of the players.  Anymore, Test is like another normal production server with a smaller population.<br>
<br>
   Why did I choose Firiona Vie?  I am hoping that the TLC and one character restriction here will keep the server more in line with what I remember Test being when I first started there.  I am looking for a place where I can come to relax, play the type of game I enjoy, and maybe make some new friends along the way.  While I do hope to get to the high-end game here, it is not the most important reason I came.  I guess I came here looking to find more of a family community again.<br>
<br>
Looking forward to meeting you all in game,<br>
Tailson     <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=seraphimmm>Seraphimmm</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.cox.net/seraphimm/boundhandsrose.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Existant
